        "\n",
        "The primary outcome of this project is to analyze daily power generation data from different power stations and regions to identify generation patterns, compare performance, and support data-driven decision-making. The analysis helps stakeholders optimize power distribution, improve operational efficiency, detect underperforming power stations, and plan for future energy demand through clear visualizations and statistical insights.\n",
